ROBOT ELECTRONICS: Repairing a robot's electronic systems

Category: Electrical
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Understanding and repairing the electronic systems inside a robot or
robot vehicle: sensor arrays, targeting computers, control systems.
Covers the electronics, not the mechanical frame - see Robot
Mechanics for that side of robot upkeep.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, electrical engineer, robot mechanics, pilot robot
